The other objects included in the collection are: Asteroid (rotating
rock-like object), Comet (with animated tail), Earth (revolving planet)
and Satellite (with rotating antennas, transmitting dishes and solar
panels). These are stored as IFF anim-brushes, and are available in NTSC
and PAL formats (the PAL versions were generated automatically from the
original NTSC versions). These objects are stored in 16 colors, but only
colors from 9 to 15 are used, so that the entries from 0 to 8 are free to
be used for ColorFonts or AnimFonts.

